/server/wapi/event_consumer_server.go` - EventConsumerServer wrapping StreamCons
umer\n   - `internal/server/wcore/wcc/event_dispatch_server.go` - EventDispatchS
erver publishes core events\n\n5. **Data layer**:\n   - `internal/data/wapi/data
.go` - Provides EventBus, StreamPublisher, IdempotencyChecker, StreamConsumer\n 
 - `internal/data/wmix/data.go` - Provides StreamPublisher\n   - `internal/data/
