se returned cancel functions** - The `bus.Subscribe` calls in `RegisterQuestSubs
criber` discard the returned cancel functions. This is acceptable for applicatio
n-lifecycle subscriptions.\n\n4. **`LoginHandler` in `internal/service/wcity/wun
i/on_login.go` has an unused `mcr` parameter** - Looking at `NewLoginHandler`, `
